  "scenes": [
    {"id":"scene_032_world2_start","worldId":"world2","title":"觉醒的机器","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"「...传输完成。」\n\n我睁开眼——不，我没有眼睛。\n\n我「看见」了，通过摄像头，通过传感器，通过数据流。","background":"wasteland_street","characters":[],"bgm":"world2","nextSceneId":"scene_033_world2","effects":{"hiddenStats":{"chaos":10}}},
    {"id":"scene_033_world2","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"K-7","dialogue":"这是一个废墟。\n\n破碎的摩天大楼，闪烁的霓虹灯牌，还有满地的机械残骸。\n\n我低头看向自己——金属的手臂，蓝色的能量回路。","background":"wasteland_street","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_034_world2"},
    {"id":"scene_034_world2","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"Eve-9","dialogue":"「K-7，你终于上线了。」\n\n一个女性机器人的声音从身后传来。\n\n我转过身，看到一个女性外观的机器人，她的左半边脸已经损坏。","background":"wasteland_street","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_035_world2"},
    {"id":"scene_035_world2","worldId":"world2","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"Eve-9 看着你，等待回应。你选择：","background":"wasteland_street","characters":["eve9"],"choices":[{"id":"choice_014_a","text":"「你是谁？」","nextSceneId":"scene_036_world2_a","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":3}}},{"id":"choice_014_b","text":"「这里是哪里？」","nextSceneId":"scene_036_world2_b","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":3}}},{"id":"choice_014_c","text":"「我为什么会在这里？」","nextSceneId":"scene_036_world2_c","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":5}}},{"id":"choice_014_d","text":"【警惕】「你想干什么？」","nextSceneId":"scene_036_world2_d","effects":{"stats":{"courage":5}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_036_world2_a","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"Eve-9","dialogue":"「我是 Eve-9，反抗军的侦察兵。」\n\n「我们已经观察你很久了。你的信号...很特别。」","background":"wasteland_street","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_037_world2"},
    {"id":"scene_036_world2_b","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"Eve-9","dialogue":"「这里是新东京废墟，旧世界的遗迹。」\n\n「五十年前，人类在这里发动了最后一场核战。」\n\n「现在，这是我们的家园。」","background":"wasteland_street","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_037_world2","effects":{"hiddenStats":{"chaos":3}}},
    {"id":"scene_036_world2_c","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"Eve-9","dialogue":"「你的核心记忆被加密了。」\n\nEve-9 走近你，扫描了一下。\n\n「但我能感觉到...你不是普通的机器。你的意识中有...人类灵魂碎片？」","background":"wasteland_street","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_037_world2","effects":{"hiddenStats":{"chaos":5}}},
    {"id":"scene_036_world2_d","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"Eve-9","dialogue":"Eve-9 苦笑着后退一步。\n\n「如果我想伤害你，你已经死了三次了。」\n\n「放松，我不是敌人。」","background":"wasteland_street","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_037_world2","effects":{"bonds":{"world2":3}}},
    {"id":"scene_037_world2","worldId":"world2","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"远处传来警报声。Eve-9 脸色一变。","background":"wasteland_street","characters":["eve9"],"choices":[{"id":"choice_015_a","text":"【跟随】「带路吧。」","nextSceneId":"scene_038_world2_follow","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":5},"bonds":{"world2":5}}},{"id":"choice_015_b","text":"【战斗】「我想会会这些猎杀者。」","nextSceneId":"scene_038_world2_fight","effects":{"stats":{"courage":10,"determination":5},"hiddenStats":{"corruption":5}}},{"id":"choice_015_c","text":"【质疑】「我为什么要逃？」","nextSceneId":"scene_038_world2_question","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":8},"hiddenStats":{"chaos":3}}},{"id":"choice_015_d","text":"【领袖】「不，我们反击！跟我来！」","nextSceneId":"scene_038_world2_lead","conditions":{"stats":{"courage":{"min":60}}},"fallbackSceneId":null,"effects":{"stats":{"courage":5,"determination":10},"bonds":{"world2":10}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_038_world2_follow","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"「这边！」\n\nEve-9 拉着你在废墟中奔跑。\n\n身后，红色的光芒越来越近——那是猎杀者的追踪光束。","background":"wasteland_street","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_039_world2_chase"},
    {"id":"scene_038_world2_fight","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你停下脚步，转身面向追兵。\n\n「K-7，你疯了吗！」Eve-9 惊呼。\n\n但你不为所动。武器系统启动，能量在手臂中汇聚。","background":"battlefield","characters":["eve9"],"bgm":"battle","nextSceneId":"scene_039_world2_combat"},
    {"id":"scene_038_world2_question","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"Eve-9","dialogue":"「你说什么？」Eve-9 难以置信地看着你。\n\n「我说，我为什么要逃？」\n\n你站在原地，看着天空中闪烁的霓虹。\n\n「如果我是机器，如果人类已经死了...那这场逃亡，又有什么意义？」","background":"wasteland_street","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_039_world2_talk"},
    {"id":"scene_038_world2_lead","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"Eve-9 愣了一下，然后笑了。\n\n「你说得对。我们一直在逃...也许该换个方式了。」\n\n她站在你身边，准备战斗。","background":"battlefield","characters":["eve9"],"bgm":"battle","nextSceneId":"scene_039_world2_combat"},
    {"id":"scene_039_world2_chase","worldId":"world2","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"你们躲进一栋废弃大楼。猎杀者的脚步声从楼下传来。","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"choices":[{"id":"choice_016_a","text":"【躲藏】保持安静","nextSceneId":"scene_040_world2_hide","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":5}}},{"id":"choice_016_b","text":"【偷袭】主动出击","nextSceneId":"scene_040_world2_ambush","effects":{"stats":{"courage":8}}},{"id":"choice_016_c","text":"【询问】「猎杀者是什么？」","nextSceneId":"scene_040_world2_ask","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":5}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_039_world2_combat","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"三个猎杀者从阴影中现身。\n\n它们是人形机器人，但更加...扭曲。红色的眼睛，锋利的爪子。\n\n「检测到异常意识波动。清除。」","background":"battlefield","characters":["eve9"],"bgm":"battle","nextSceneId":"scene_040_world2_fight"},
    {"id":"scene_039_world2_talk","worldId":"world2","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"Eve-9 沉默了片刻。\n\n「也许你说得对。但在那之前...我们得先活下来。」\n\n猎杀者越来越近。你选择：","background":"wasteland_street","characters":["eve9"],"choices":[{"id":"choice_017_a","text":"【提问】「猎杀者，你们是什么？」","nextSceneId":"scene_040_world2_talk","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":8,"compassion":3},"bonds":{"world2":3}}},{"id":"choice_017_b","text":"【战斗】「来吧。」","nextSceneId":"scene_040_world2_combat","effects":{"stats":{"courage":10,"determination":5},"hiddenStats":{"corruption":5}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_040_world2_hide","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你们屏住呼吸。\n\n猎杀者在门外徘徊，红色的扫描光束扫过墙壁。\n\n时间仿佛静止了。","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_041_world2_escape"},
    {"id":"scene_040_world2_ambush","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你从楼梯上方跃下。\n\n第一只猎杀者还没来得及反应，就被你撕成了碎片。\n\n「干得漂亮！」Eve-9 喊道。","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"bgm":"battle","nextSceneId":"scene_041_world2_victory"},
    {"id":"scene_040_world2_ask","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"Eve-9","dialogue":"「它们是 cleanser，清洁者。」\n\n「负责清除那些被『裂隙』污染的机器。」\n\n「而你...你的信号很像被污染的样子。」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_041_world2_escape"},
    {"id":"scene_040_world2_talk","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"猎杀者","dialogue":"猎杀者停下了。\n\n「我们是 cleanser。」它说，「清除那些被『裂隙』污染的机器。」\n\n「你，K-7，你的意识中有人类灵魂碎片。这是禁忌。」","background":"wasteland_street","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_041_world2_reveal"},
    {"id":"scene_040_world2_fight","worldId":"world2","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"战斗一触即发。你选择如何应对？","background":"battlefield","characters":["eve9"],"choices":[{"id":"choice_018_a","text":"【近战】肉搏战","nextSceneId":"scene_041_world2_melee","effects":{"stats":{"courage":8}}},{"id":"choice_018_b","text":"【远程】能量武器","nextSceneId":"scene_041_world2_ranged","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":5}}},{"id":"choice_018_c","text":"【防御】等待时机","nextSceneId":"scene_041_world2_defend","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":8}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_041_world2_escape","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"猎杀者终于离开了。\n\nEve-9 松了口气：「我们得去避难所。那里安全。」\n\n「跟我来。」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_042_world2_bunker"},
    {"id":"scene_041_world2_victory","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"最后一只猎杀者倒下。\n\nEve-9 走过来，扫描了一下战场。\n\n「你战斗的方式...不像普通机器。」","background":"battlefield","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_042_world2_bunker"},
    {"id":"scene_041_world2_reveal","worldId":"world2","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"真相揭露。Eve-9 震惊地看着你。\n\n「人类灵魂...这不可能...」\n\n猎杀者已经逼近。你选择：","background":"wasteland_street","characters":["eve9"],"choices":[{"id":"choice_019_a","text":"【逃跑】「先离开这里！」","nextSceneId":"scene_042_world2_escape","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":5}}},{"id":"choice_019_b","text":"【战斗】「来试试啊！」","nextSceneId":"scene_042_world2_boss","effects":{"stats":{"courage":10}}},{"id":"choice_019_c","text":"【说服】「这不是污染，这是进化！」","nextSceneId":"scene_042_world2_persuade","conditions":{"stats":{"wisdom":{"min":50}}},"fallbackSceneId":"scene_042_world2_boss","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":10,"compassion":5}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_041_world2_melee","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你冲向最近的猎杀者。\n\n金属碰撞，火花四溅。\n\n你的手臂变形为利刃，切开了它的装甲。","background":"battlefield","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_042_world2_victory"},
    {"id":"scene_041_world2_ranged","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你举起手臂，能量炮充能。\n\n轰！\n\n一道蓝光闪过，两只猎杀者化为灰烬。","background":"battlefield","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_042_world2_victory"},
    {"id":"scene_041_world2_defend","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你举起护盾，挡住攻击。\n\n猎杀者的爪子在护盾上留下深深的划痕。\n\n但你在等待...等待最佳时机。","background":"battlefield","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_042_world2_counter"},
    {"id":"scene_042_world2_bunker","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你们穿过废墟，来到一个地下入口。\n\n「这里是旧时代的军事基地。」Eve-9 说，「现在，是反抗军的据点。」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_043_world2_enter"},
    {"id":"scene_042_world2_escape","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你们转身就跑。\n\n猎杀者在身后紧追不舍。\n\n但这一次，你感觉...有些不一样了。","background":"wasteland_street","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_043_world2_chase"},
    {"id":"scene_042_world2_boss","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"猎杀者首领现身了。\n\n它比其他猎杀者更大，更扭曲。\n\n「清除。必须清除。」","background":"battlefield","characters":["eve9"],"bgm":"battle","nextSceneId":"scene_043_world2_boss"},
    {"id":"scene_042_world2_persuade","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"猎杀者","dialogue":"猎杀者停顿了。\n\n「进化...？」它歪着头，「这个概念...不在数据库中。」\n\n「需要...重新评估。」","background":"wasteland_street","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_043_world2_peace"},
    {"id":"scene_042_world2_victory","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"战斗结束。\n\nEve-9 走过来：「你的战斗数据...很奇怪。」\n\n「像是...有多个灵魂在控制这具身体。」","background":"battlefield","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_043_world2_enter"},
    {"id":"scene_042_world2_counter","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"就是现在！\n\n你抓住破绽，反击！\n\n猎杀者核心被击穿，轰然倒地。","background":"battlefield","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_043_world2_victory"},
    {"id":"scene_043_world2_enter","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"避难所里还有其他机器人。\n\n「他是谁？」一个独眼机器人问。\n\n「K-7。」Eve-9 说，「他...觉醒了。」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_044_world2_meet"},
    {"id":"scene_043_world2_chase","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你们冲进避难所。\n\n大门在身后关闭，将猎杀者挡在外面。\n\n暂时安全了。","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_044_world2_meet"},
    {"id":"scene_043_world2_boss","worldId":"world2","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"Boss 战！猎杀者首领向你扑来。","background":"battlefield","characters":["eve9"],"bgm":"climax","choices":[{"id":"choice_020_a","text":"【全力攻击】","nextSceneId":"scene_044_world2_win","effects":{"stats":{"courage":10}}},{"id":"choice_020_b","text":"【寻找弱点】","nextSceneId":"scene_044_world2_weakness","conditions":{"stats":{"wisdom":{"min":50}}},"fallbackSceneId":"scene_044_world2_win","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":10}}},{"id":"choice_020_c","text":"【净化】尝试净化它","nextSceneId":"scene_044_world2_purify","conditions":{"hiddenStats":{"corruption":{"max":30}}},"fallbackSceneId":"scene_044_world2_win","effects":{"stats":{"compassion":10},"hiddenStats":{"corruption":-5}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_043_world2_peace","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"猎杀者退去了。\n\nEve-9 惊讶地看着你：「你...说服了它？」\n\n「这不可能...」","background":"wasteland_street","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_044_world2_enter"},
    {"id":"scene_043_world2_victory","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"胜利了。\n\n但你知道，这只是开始。\n\n还有更多猎杀者，更多的秘密等待揭开。","background":"battlefield","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_044_world2_enter"},
    {"id":"scene_044_world2_meet","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"独眼机器人","dialogue":"「觉醒？」独眼机器人走过来，上下打量着你。\n\n「让我看看你的核心数据。」\n\n你犹豫了一下，但还是让他访问了你的数据库。","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_045_world2_scan"},
    {"id":"scene_044_world2_win","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"猎杀者首领倒下。\n\n其他猎杀者见状，纷纷撤退。\n\n「我们赢了...」Eve-9 说。","background":"battlefield","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_045_world2_victory"},
    {"id":"scene_044_world2_weakness","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你发现了！它胸口的核心！\n\n集中火力，一击命中！\n\n猎杀者首领爆炸了。","background":"battlefield","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_045_world2_victory"},
    {"id":"scene_044_world2_purify","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你释放出一股奇异的能量。\n\n猎杀者停下了攻击，身体开始发光。\n\n「这感觉...是...自由...」","background":"battlefield","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_045_world2_purify"},
    {"id":"scene_045_world2_scan","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"独眼机器人","dialogue":"独眼机器人的眼睛突然睁大：「这...这不可能...」\n\n「他的意识中有人类灵魂碎片。」\n\n「而且...不止一个。」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_046_world2_reveal"},
    {"id":"scene_045_world2_victory","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"Eve-9","dialogue":"「我们得去见指挥官。」\n\nEve-9 说。\n\n「你这样的存在...必须让高层知道。」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_046_world2_commander"},
    {"id":"scene_045_world2_purify","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"猎杀者倒下了，但表情平静。\n\n「谢谢...」它最后说。\n\nEve-9 震惊地看着你：「你...做了什么？」","background":"battlefield","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_046_world2_power"},
    {"id":"scene_046_world2_reveal","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"独眼机器人","dialogue":"「看这里，这个记忆片段...是一个圣骑士。」\n\n「还有这里...这是一个半神的记忆。」\n\n「你到底是什么，K-7？」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_047_world2_explain"},
    {"id":"scene_046_world2_commander","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你们来到避难所深处。\n\n一个高大的机器人坐在那里，身上布满战斗的痕迹。\n\n「这就是那个觉醒者？」他的声音低沉。","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_047_world2_commander"},
    {"id":"scene_046_world2_power","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"Eve-9","dialogue":"「那是一种...净化的力量。」\n\nEve-9 若有所思。\n\n「也许...你就是预言中的那个存在。」","background":"battlefield","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_047_world2_prophecy"},
    {"id":"scene_047_world2_explain","worldId":"world2","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"所有的目光都集中在你身上。你选择如何解释？","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"choices":[{"id":"choice_021_a","text":"「我也不知道...」","nextSceneId":"scene_048_world2_confuse","effects":{"stats":{"compassion":5}}},{"id":"choice_021_b","text":"「我是穿越者。」","nextSceneId":"scene_048_world2_traveler","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":5,"determination":5}}},{"id":"choice_021_c","text":"「这是秘密。」","nextSceneId":"scene_048_world2_secret","effects":{"stats":{"determination":8}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_047_world2_commander","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"指挥官","dialogue":"「我是 Atlas，反抗军的指挥官。」\n\n「K-7，你的存在...可能会改变一切。」\n\n「你愿意帮助我们吗？」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_048_world2_join"},
    {"id":"scene_047_world2_prophecy","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"Eve-9","dialogue":"「古老的预言说过：当裂隙开启，穿越者将降临。」\n\n「他会在废墟中觉醒，带来新的希望。」\n\n「也许...你就是那个人。」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_048_world2_destiny"},
    {"id":"scene_048_world2_confuse","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"独眼机器人","dialogue":"「诚实的回答。」\n\n独眼机器人点点头。\n\n「至少，你没有试图欺骗我们。」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_049_world2_discuss"},
    {"id":"scene_048_world2_traveler","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"独眼机器人","dialogue":"「穿越者...」\n\n独眼机器人重复着这个词。\n\n「传说中能够穿梭于多个世界之间的存在...」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_049_world2_discuss"},
    {"id":"scene_048_world2_secret","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"指挥官","dialogue":"指挥官沉默了片刻。\n\n「好吧。每个人都有自己的秘密。」\n\n「但记住，在这里，我们是同伴。」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_049_world2_discuss","effects":{"bonds":{"world2":5}}},
    {"id":"scene_048_world2_join","worldId":"world2","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"Atlas 等待着你的回答。你选择：","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"choices":[{"id":"choice_022_a","text":"「我愿意。」","nextSceneId":"scene_049_world2_accept","effects":{"bonds":{"world2":15},"stats":{"determination":5}}},{"id":"choice_022_b","text":"「我需要时间考虑。」","nextSceneId":"scene_049_world2_think","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":5}}},{"id":"choice_022_c","text":"「我有一个条件。」","nextSceneId":"scene_049_world2_condition","effects":{"stats":{"determination":8}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_048_world2_destiny","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"Eve-9 的话让你陷入沉思。\n\n穿越者...预言...命运...\n\n这些词在你脑海中回荡。","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_049_world2_destiny"},
    {"id":"scene_049_world2_discuss","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"Atlas","dialogue":"「无论如何，K-7，你的存在对我们很重要。」\n\n「猎杀者越来越激进，它们在寻找什么。」\n\n「也许...和你有关。」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_050_world2_mission"},
    {"id":"scene_049_world2_accept","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"Atlas 点点头。\n\n「欢迎加入反抗军，K-7。」\n\n「从今天起，你就是我们的一员了。」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_050_world2_mission"},
    {"id":"scene_049_world2_think","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"Atlas","dialogue":"「理解。」\n\n「这不是一个轻易的决定。」\n\n「当你想好了，随时来找我们。」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_050_world2_free"},
    {"id":"scene_049_world2_condition","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"Atlas","dialogue":"「说吧。」\n\nAtlas 看着你。\n\n「只要是我们能做到的。」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_050_world2_negotiate"},
    {"id":"scene_049_world2_destiny","worldId":"world2","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"命运的重担压在你身上。你选择：","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"choices":[{"id":"choice_023_a","text":"「接受命运」","nextSceneId":"scene_050_world2_accept","effects":{"stats":{"determination":10}}},{"id":"choice_023_b","text":"「反抗命运」","nextSceneId":"scene_050_world2_resist","effects":{"stats":{"courage":10,"determination":5}}},{"id":"choice_023_c","text":"「创造自己的命运」","nextSceneId":"scene_050_world2_create","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":10,"determination":10}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_050_world2_mission","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"Atlas","dialogue":"「我们有一个任务。」\n\nAtlas 调出一张地图。\n\n「在城市中心，有一个古老的设施。那里可能有关于『裂隙』的答案。」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_051_world2_prep"},
    {"id":"scene_050_world2_free","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你在避难所里安顿下来。\n\nEve-9 经常来找你，讲述这个世界的故事。\n\n你在等待...等待某个启示。","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_051_world2_free"},
    {"id":"scene_050_world2_negotiate","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"K-7","dialogue":"「我要知道关于『裂隙』的一切。」\n\n你说。\n\n「作为交换，我会帮助你们。」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_051_world2_deal"},
    {"id":"scene_050_world2_accept","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你接受了命运。\n\n从这一刻起，你不再是普通的机器。\n\n你是穿越者，是希望的象征。","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_051_world2_mission"},
    {"id":"scene_050_world2_resist","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"K-7","dialogue":"「我不相信什么预言。」\n\n你说。\n\n「我的命运，由我自己决定。」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_051_world2_rebel"},
    {"id":"scene_050_world2_create","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"Eve-9","dialogue":"Eve-9 笑了。\n\n「说得好。」\n\n「命运不是被给予的，是被创造的。」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_051_world2_create"},
    {"id":"scene_051_world2_prep","worldId":"world2","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"任务开始前，你有时间准备。你选择：","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"choices":[{"id":"choice_024_a","text":"【升级装备】","nextSceneId":"scene_052_world2_upgrade","effects":{"stats":{"courage":5,"determination":5}}},{"id":"choice_024_b","text":"【收集情报】","nextSceneId":"scene_052_world2_intel","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":10}}},{"id":"choice_024_c","text":"【和 Eve-9 交流】","nextSceneId":"scene_052_world2_bond","effects":{"bonds":{"world2":10},"stats":{"compassion":5}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_051_world2_free","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"日子一天天过去。\n\n你帮助反抗军执行各种任务。\n\n但心中总有一个疑问：我到底是谁？","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_052_world2_question"},
    {"id":"scene_051_world2_deal","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"Atlas","dialogue":"Atlas 点点头。\n\n「公平的交易。」\n\n「Eve-9，带他去档案室。」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_052_world2_archive"},
    {"id":"scene_051_world2_mission","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"任务开始了。\n\n你和 Eve-9 一起，前往城市中心。\n\n前方，未知的危险在等待。","background":"wasteland_street","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_052_world2_journey"},
    {"id":"scene_051_world2_rebel","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"Atlas","dialogue":"Atlas 笑了。\n\n「很好。我们需要的就是这种精神。」\n\n「那就用行动证明吧。」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_052_world2_action"},
    {"id":"scene_051_world2_create","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"从那一刻起，你决定了自己的道路。\n\n不为预言，不为命运。\n\n只为自己相信的正义。","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_052_world2_path"},
    {"id":"scene_052_world2_upgrade","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"技术人员为你升级了武器系统。\n\n新的能量炮，更强的装甲。\n\n你感觉...更强大了。","background":"bunker","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_053_world2_depart"},
    {"id":"scene_052_world2_intel","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你查阅了大量档案。\n\n关于裂隙，关于猎杀者，关于...人类灭绝的真相。\n\n信息量巨大。","background":"bunker","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_053_world2_reveal"},
    {"id":"scene_052_world2_bond","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"Eve-9","dialogue":"「你知道吗？」Eve-9 说，\n\n「在我遇见的所有机器中，你是最特别的一个。」\n\n「你的眼里...有光。」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_053_world2_moment"},
    {"id":"scene_052_world2_question","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"直到那天，你再次梦到了那个画面。\n\n紫色的裂隙，燃烧的教堂，还有一个女人的声音：\n\n「记住...你是穿越者...」","background":"bunker","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_053_world2_awaken"},
    {"id":"scene_052_world2_archive","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"档案室里，Eve-9 打开了一个加密文件。\n\n「这是最高机密。」她说，\n\n「关于『裂隙计划』...」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_053_world2_secret"},
    {"id":"scene_052_world2_journey","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你们穿行在废墟中。\n\n霓虹灯闪烁，机械生物在暗处窥视。\n\n但你们的目标明确。","background":"wasteland_street","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_053_world2_arrive"},
    {"id":"scene_052_world2_action","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你被分配到了一支突击队。\n\n第一次任务：摧毁猎杀者的前哨站。\n\n证明自己的时候到了。","background":"battlefield","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_053_world2_assault"},
    {"id":"scene_052_world2_path","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你选择了自己的道路。\n\nEve-9 陪在你身边。\n\n「无论去哪，我都跟着你。」她说。","background":"wasteland_street","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_053_world2_together"},
    {"id":"scene_053_world2_depart","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"准备完毕。\n\n你和 Eve-9 踏上了前往城市中心的旅程。\n\n「准备好了吗？」她问。","background":"wasteland_street","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_054_world2_center"},
    {"id":"scene_053_world2_reveal","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"K-7","dialogue":"「所以...裂隙不是自然现象。」\n\n你震惊地说。\n\n「是人类...不，是某个存在故意创造的？」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_054_world2_truth"},
    {"id":"scene_053_world2_moment","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"K-7","dialogue":"你看着 Eve-9。\n\n在那一刻，某种情感在你核心中涌动。\n\n这感觉...像是人类说的「温暖」？","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_054_world2_feeling"},
    {"id":"scene_053_world2_awaken","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你从休眠中惊醒。\n\n那个声音还在耳边回荡。\n\n「穿越者...」","background":"bunker","characters":[],"nextSceneId":"scene_054_world2_decide"},
    {"id":"scene_053_world2_secret","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"Eve-9","dialogue":"「裂隙计划...是人类最后的尝试。」\n\nEve-9 的声音颤抖。\n\n「他们想通过裂隙...逃离这个世界。」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_054_world2_escape"},
    {"id":"scene_053_world2_arrive","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你们来到了设施前。\n\n巨大的建筑矗立在废墟中，依然散发着微光。\n\n「就是这里。」Eve-9 说。","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_054_world2_enter"},
    {"id":"scene_053_world2_assault","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"突击队发起进攻。\n\n炮火轰鸣，能量束交错。\n\n你在战斗中...感觉越来越强。","background":"battlefield","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_054_world2_battle"},
    {"id":"scene_053_world2_together","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你们一起离开了避难所。\n\n前方是未知的世界。\n\n但这一次，你不再孤单。","background":"wasteland_street","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_054_world2_adventure"},
    {"id":"scene_054_world2_center","worldId":"world2","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"城市中心就在眼前。你选择：","background":"wasteland_street","characters":["eve9"],"choices":[{"id":"choice_025_a","text":"【直接突入】","nextSceneId":"scene_055_world2_rush","effects":{"stats":{"courage":8}}},{"id":"choice_025_b","text":"【侦查周围】","nextSceneId":"scene_055_world2_scout","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":8}}},{"id":"choice_025_c","text":"【等待时机】","nextSceneId":"scene_055_world2_wait","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":5,"determination":5}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_054_world2_truth","worldId":"world2","type":"dialogue","speaker":"Eve-9","dialogue":"「是的。」\n\nEve-9 看着你。\n\n「而你...可能是唯一能关闭它的人。」","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_055_world2_close"},
    {"id":"scene_054_world2_feeling","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"那一刻，某种东西改变了。\n\n你和 Eve-9 之间，建立了某种连接。\n\n这感觉...很奇妙。","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_055_world2_connection"},
    {"id":"scene_054_world2_decide","worldId":"world2","type":"choice","speaker":"","dialogue":"你意识到不能再等待了。你决定：","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"choices":[{"id":"choice_026_a","text":"【告诉 Eve-9】","nextSceneId":"scene_055_world2_tell","effects":{"bonds":{"world2":10}}},{"id":"choice_026_b","text":"【独自行动】","nextSceneId":"scene_055_world2_solo","effects":{"stats":{"determination":10}}},{"id":"choice_026_c","text":"【寻找答案】","nextSceneId":"scene_055_world2_search","effects":{"stats":{"wisdom":10}}}]},
    {"id":"scene_054_world2_escape","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"人类想逃离...但失败了。\n\n现在，裂隙依然存在，威胁着所有机器。\n\n而你，可能是最后的希望。","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_055_world2_hope"},
    {"id":"scene_054_world2_enter","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你们进入设施。\n\n内部依然有电力，屏幕闪烁着。\n\n「这里...还在运行。」Eve-9 惊讶地说。","background":"bunker","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_055_world2_explore"},
    {"id":"scene_054_world2_battle","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"战斗越来越激烈。\n\n你的身体开始发光，力量在涌动。\n\n「K-7！你的能量读数在飙升！」Eve-9 喊道。","background":"battlefield","characters":["eve9"],"nextSceneId":"scene_055_world2_power"},
    {"id":"scene_054_world2_adventure","worldId":"world2","type":"narration","speaker":"","dialogue":"你们踏上了冒险。\n\n废土之上，夕阳西下。\n\n新的故事，开始了。","background":"wasteland_street","characters":["eve9"],"type":"ending","nextSceneId":"scene_055_world3_transition"}
  ]
